#: ../../../doc/en/index.rst:45
msgid ""
"The ``pytest`` framework makes it easy to write small, readable tests, and "
"can scale to support complex functional testing for applications and "
"libraries."
msgstr ""
"``pytest`` 框架讓編寫小型且具可讀性的測試變得容易，並能擴展以支援應用程式與程"
"式庫的複雜功能測試。"

